&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h2&gt;Join us in building the future of finance.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our mission is to democratize finance for all. &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.cerulli.com/press-releases/cerulli-anticipates-124-trillion-in-wealth-will-transfer-through-2048&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;An estimated $124 trillion of assets&lt;/a&gt; will be inherited by younger generations in the next two decades. The largest transfer of wealth in human history. If you’re ready to be at the epicenter of this historic cultural and financial shift, keep reading.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Team &amp;amp; Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are building an elite team, applying frontier technologies to the world’s biggest financial problems. We’re looking for bold thinkers. Sharp problem-solvers. Builders who are wired to make an impact. Robinhood isn’t a place for complacency, it’s where ambitious people do the best work of their careers. We’re a high-performing, fast-moving team with ethics at the center of everything we do. Expectations are high, and so are the rewards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Prediction Markets team at Robinhood is dedicated to delivering a premier trading experience and establishing Robinhood as the leader in the event contracts space. Enabling our customers to trade on the outcome of real-world events aligns directly with our mission to democratize finance for all! We collaborate closely with product managers, designers, and operations specialists to build state-of-the-art trading experiences across a wide variety of real-world events. Our team culture values technical excellence, operational rigor, and a strong sense of collective accountability for our products.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the Engineering Manager for Prediction Markets, you will lead a team of software engineers focused on building the complete user experience for key US and global events. In this leadership position, you will serve as a key partner in growing this business, which represents the fastest-growing segment in Robinhood’s history! You will oversee the delivery of scalable UIs that enable customers to trade on diverse categories such as financials, crypto, sports, and politics. Additionally, you will guide technical architecture, mentor engineers, and help define how the event contracts space evolves across the industry.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This role is based in our New York, NY office, with in-person attendance expected at least 5 days per week.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At Robinhood, we believe in the power of in-person work to accelerate progress, spark innovation, and strengthen community. Our office experience is intentional, energizing, and designed to fully support high-performing teams.&lt;/p&gt;
