&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead and support a team of software engineers in owning all consumer-facing features for our prediction markets product.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Be a thought leader with product managers, designers, and operations partners to design and launch trading experiences for major global events.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define technical roadmaps, establish coding standards, and maintain operational excellence for our prediction market systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor and develop engineers on the team, helping them progress in their careers and achieve technical excellence.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
